Reira, are you all right?

252
00:16:34,063 --> 00:16:36,553
Please do me a favor.

253
00:16:38,463 --> 00:16:39,293
I'm sorry.

254
00:16:39,563 --> 00:16:42,033
Just tell me what it is.
I'll do anything.

255
00:16:47,773 --> 00:16:49,863
I don't need any more money.

256
00:16:53,743 --> 00:16:54,573
Yasu, .,

257
00:16:54,743 --> 00:16:55,373
Huh?

258
00:16:58,653 --> 00:16:59,273
What?

259
00:17:00,953 --> 00:17:04,393
Please give me Yasu's cell number.

260
00:18:36,113 --> 00:18:36,783
Hello...

261
00:18:36,783 --> 00:18:41,113
Nana?! What the hell are you doing?!
You had me worried!

262
00:18:41,623 --> 00:18:42,313
Nobu?

263
00:18:42,453 --> 00:18:43,923
I called you a number of times
since this morning,

264
00:18:43,923 --> 00:18:45,013
but you didn't pick up!

265
00:18:45,193 --> 00:18:47,683
I was panicking a bit last night
and said some mean things.

266
00:18:48,063 --> 00:18:51,163
But I'm the one this is happening to
and went to work today,

267
00:18:51,163 --> 00:18:52,563
so how dare you take the day off!

268
00:18:52,963 --> 00:18:54,953
I'm starting to hate myself
for being so damn responsible.

269
00:18:55,363 --> 00:18:57,393
MISSED CALL NOBUO
MISSED CALL NOBUO
