296
00:20:55,453 --> 00:20:56,583
LOVELY LAYLA

297
00:21:00,763 --> 00:21:02,493
I was just too fragile.

298
00:21:04,293 --> 00:21:05,733
It's not your fault.

299
00:21:09,303 --> 00:21:15,203
I can't count
how many nights

300
00:21:15,273 --> 00:21:19,973
I wished tomorrow
would never come

301
00:21:20,043 --> 00:21:26,743
To live as I am
without being fake

302
00:21:26,823 --> 00:21:30,343
What do I need

303
00:21:32,823 --> 00:21:38,493
If I don't believe in myself,
what can I believe in

304
00:21:38,563 --> 00:21:43,663
The answer is
too close to see

305
00:21:43,733 --> 00:21:49,903
Black tears are
falling down

306
00:21:49,973 --> 00:21:56,843
I have nothing,
only sadness

307
00:21:56,913 --> 00:22:01,943
I can't put it
into words

308
00:22:02,023 --> 00:22:08,013
My whole body
starts to ache

309
00:22:08,093 --> 00:22:13,433
I can't stand it anymore
on my own

